2013-14 Bridging Year data has been sourced from the PSS-EX1 return for that year and then calculated by the HSCIC.
2013-14 Actual total net cost have not been calculated for regions or England due to number of councils with data not available.

Please note: Whilst comparisons have been made to the grand total and the totals for the two age groups, the  additional categories for 2014-15 and 2013-14 data may not be comparable when considering the differences between years, but do provide information as to how these totals have been calculated.
Please note: Data quality issues affecting primary support reasons have been reported by some councils, see Appendix B in the report for this publication for further information.
